                </center>

                <p class="sm_highlight" style="margin: 5px 0px;color: #2372BF !important;">
                    The tentative schedule of the ceremony is as follows:
                </p>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        • Registration confirmation @ respective department counters : 08.30 a.m. to 09.30 a.m.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        • Collection of Graduation Robes and Registration for photos : 08.30 a.m. to 09.30 a.m.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        • Occupying allotted Seat in the Hall : 09.30 a.m.
                    </li>
                </ul>

                <p>
                    The graduands are asked to pay Rs.600/- towards caution deposit for Graduation Robes (Rs.500/- will
                    be refunded on return of Graduation Robes) and Rs.300/- for Graduation Photo of the Individual in
                    the respective counters.
                </p>

                <p class="sm_highlight" style="margin: 5px 0px;color: #2372BF !important;">
                    NOTE:
                </p>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        1. All Graduands shall come only in formal attire.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        2. No one shall enter the Ceremony Hall after 9.30 a.m.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        3. All Graduands shall handover the Mobile Phones at the Registration Desk.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        4. No spot registration.
                    </li>
                </ul>

                <p>
                    All the eligible graduands, attending the ceremony, are requested to be present and register at
                    least an hour prior to the commencement of the proceedings.
                </p>

                <center>
                    <p class="sm_highlight" style="color: #F8A22E !important;">
                        “Kindly confirm your participation by filling up this registration form.” Also inform your
                        classmates to
                        register.
                    </p>
                    <p>------Registeration Closed------</p>
                </center>

                <div class="submit_btn" style="margin: 10px 0px; visibility: hidden;">
                    <button class="signin" id="redirectButton">------Registeration Closed------</button>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>



        <div class="footer">
            <ul>
                <li><a href="https://skct.edu.in">skct.edu.in</a></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
